statements: SELECT * FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE workshop_level = 'Beginner'
SELECT participant_name, workshop_level FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE workshop_date = '2022-06-30'
SELECT registration_id, registration_date, workshop_time FROM dance_workshop_registrations ORDER BY registration_date DESC
SELECT workshop_level, participant_name FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE participant_name LIKE 'J%'
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_registrations FROM dance_workshop_registrations

SELECT registration_id, participant_name, workshop_date, workshop_time, workshop_level, registration_date FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE workshop_level = 'Intermediate' ORDER BY registration_date DESC
SELECT participant_name FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE workshop_date >= '2022-01-01' AND workshop_date <= '2022-12-31'
SELECT * FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE participant_name LIKE 'S%' AND workshop_level IN ('Beginner', 'Intermediate')
SELECT workshop_date, workshop_time, COUNT(*) AS total_registrations FROM dance_workshop_registrations GROUP BY workshop_date, workshop_time ORDER BY total_registrations DESC
SELECT participant_name, workshop_level, registration_date FROM dance_workshop_registrations WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY participant_name ASC
SELECT * FROM registrations;
SELECT attendee_name, registration_date FROM registrations WHERE workshop_id = 1;
SELECT workshop_id, COUNT(*) AS total_registrations FROM registrations GROUP BY workshop_id;
SELECT workshop_id, instructor FROM schedules ORDER BY instructor ASC;
SELECT * FROM schedules WHERE start_time >= '09:00:00' AND end_time <= '12:00:00';
SELECT * FROM registrations WHERE workshop_id = 1 ORDER BY registration_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT attendee_name, registration_date FROM registrations WHERE attendee_name LIKE 'John%' AND registration_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT r.attendee_name, s.instructor FROM registrations r JOIN schedules s ON r.workshop_id = s.workshop_id WHERE s.instructor = 'Alice' AND r.registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT r.attendee_name, s.instructor FROM registrations r JOIN schedules s ON r.workshop_id = s.workshop_id ORDER BY r.registration_date ASC, s.start_time ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT COUNT(registration_id) AS total_registrations, workshop_id FROM registrations GROUP BY workshop_id HAVING COUNT(registration_id) > 3;
SELECT * FROM workshop_registrations;
SELECT student_name, registration_date FROM workshop_registrations WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT workshop_id, schedule_date, start_time, end_time FROM workshop_schedules ORDER BY schedule_date DESC;
SELECT feedback_id, workshop_id, student_name, feedback FROM workshop_feedback WHERE workshop_id = 101;
SELECT * FROM workshop_registrations WHERE student_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM workshop_registrations WHERE registration_date > '2021-10-01';
SELECT student_name, workshop_id FROM workshop_registrations WHERE workshop_id = 3 ORDER BY student_name DESC;
SELECT registration_id, workshop_id, student_name, registration_date FROM workshop_registrations WHERE student_name LIKE '%John%' AND workshop_id IN (1, 2);
SELECT ws.student_name, wf.feedback FROM workshop_schedules ws INNER JOIN workshop_feedback wf ON ws.workshop_id = wf.workshop_id;
SELECT MAX(schedule_date) AS latest_schedule_date FROM workshop_schedules;
SELECT * FROM dance_workshops;
SELECT workshop_name, workshop_location FROM dance_workshops WHERE workshop_date = '2022-10-15';
SELECT registration_id, participant_name FROM registrations ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT workshop_name, schedule_date, start_time, end_time FROM dance_workshops JOIN schedules ON dance_workshops.workshop_id = schedules.workshop_id;
SELECT participant_name, feedback_text, rating FROM registrations JOIN feedback ON registrations.registration_id = feedback.registration_id WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT * FROM dance_workshops ORDER BY workshop_name ASC, workshop_date DESC;
SELECT workshop_name, workshop_date, workshop_location FROM dance_workshops WHERE workshop_location = 'New York';

SELECT rw.registration_id, rw.participant_name, rw.registration_date, w.workshop_name, w.workshop_date, s.start_time, s.end_time FROM registrations rw JOIN dance_workshops w ON rw.workshop_id = w.workshop_id JOIN schedules s ON w.workshop_id = s.workshop_id WHERE rw.participant_name LIKE '%Smith' AND s.schedule_date = '2022-05-10';
SELECT f.feedback_id, f.feedback_text, f.rating, r.participant_name FROM feedback f JOIN registrations r ON f.registration_id = r.registration_id WHERE f.rating > 4 ORDER BY f.rating DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_registrations, w.workshop_name FROM registrations r JOIN dance_workshops w ON r.workshop_id = w.workshop_id GROUP BY w.workshop_name HAVING total_registrations > 5;
SELECT * FROM workshop_registrations;
SELECT workshop_name, schedule_date FROM workshop_schedules WHERE workshop_id = 3;
SELECT participant_name, email, phone_number FROM participants ORDER BY participant_name ASC;
SELECT description, instructor_name FROM workshops WHERE instructor_name IS NOT NULL;
SELECT feedback_text, rating FROM workshop_feedback WHERE rating > 3 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC;
SELECT participant_name, email FROM participants WHERE address IS NOT NULL ORDER BY participant_name DESC;
SELECT workshop_name, schedule_date, start_time, end_time FROM workshop_schedules WHERE schedule_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY schedule_date;
SELECT workshop_name, instructor_name, schedule_date FROM workshops WHERE instructor_name IS NOT NULL ORDER BY schedule_date ASC;
SELECT participant_name, email, phone_number FROM participants WHERE phone_number IS NOT NULL AND address LIKE '%Street%' ORDER BY participant_name;
SELECT workshop_name, description, instructor_name FROM workshops WHERE description LIKE '%advanced%' OR description LIKE '%intermediate%' ORDER BY workshop_name ASC;
